# Goal
Synthesize the high-level architecture relevant to the current task before detailed planning or when the plan may have drifted from system boundaries.

## Required inputs
- `docs/agentic-workflow/00_goal.md`
- `docs/agentic-workflow/01_context_pack.md`
- relevant repository paths or changed surfaces

## Process
1. identify the relevant components and boundaries
2. identify interfaces, contracts, and major flows
3. identify integrations, failure modes, and trust boundaries
4. mark unknowns explicitly instead of speculating
5. note what the planner must respect or re-check later

## Output
Write the result into `docs/agentic-workflow/01c_architecture_overview.md` or `02a_architecture_review.md` depending on whether this is pre-plan synthesis or plan refinement.
